  "title": "SALES EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>- Handling of existing customers accounts and relationship in Pharmaceutical, Diagnostic industry (80%)</p><p>- Development of new customers in Pharmaceutical, Diagnostic, Chemical Industry (20%)</p><p>- Liaising with Japan suppliers and HQ regarding technical specifications of products</p><p>- Preparation of quotations, clarification of technical specifications with customers</p><p>- Establish clear short and long-term goals for the business</p><p>- Preparing monthly sales reports and forecast</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Chemistry or Biochemistry graduates in university are preferred, graduates from others are also welcome to apply  </p><p>- No experience / have experience of relevant sales experience in chemical Industry</p><p>- Japanese Language skills will be an advantage but not compulsory</p><p>- Experience in Japanese working environment will be advantages</p><p>- Overseas trips to regional countries such as India etc</p><p><strong>Other Details:</strong></p><p>Working Hours: 9:00am ~ 17:30pm (Mon ~ Fri)</p><p>Annual Leaves: 12days (1st year to 2nd year) - 15days (after 2nd year)</p><p>Medical Leaves: 14 days</p><p>Medical benefits: S$500/Year (1st year to 3rd year) - S$800/Year (6th Year)</p><p>Transport Allowance: NA</p><p>AWS & Variable Bonus: Provided (Based on personal and company performance)</p><p>Monthly salary: S$4,500-S$5,500</p><p>Starting: ASAP</p>",
